connect20/sku_auto_generator.name: connect20/SKU_Auto_Generator

suggest.magento-hackathon/magento-composer-insta: Allows to manage this package as a dependency

connect20/sku_auto_generator.description: Automatically create SKUs for products that are manually added via admin or imported via CSV of XML files for admin. This is ideal for stores that do not have a fixed SKU coming in from external ERP systems or their suppliers. The extension works on both Enterprise and Community Editions.
